{"tid":760702,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"放題戰略討論","createTime":"2018-07-29T18:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T09:33:55.000Z","uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9a72171071f60bd08e94cde002c27b7c102f94","tid":760702,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"其實食放題點樣先可以食到最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該食熱野定沙律先，會令到自己可以食多啲好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人策略：搵熱中湯飲左少少先，再食其他野，魚生唔好博命食，去到咁上下要食左熱野再戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲交流吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953b57a7fd48b239cf1714a4d6249ff450bce877","tid":760702,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"我諗日式放題最貴都係魚生/海鮮類<br />\n<br />\n最好唔好去扣單既放題<br />\n例如觀塘x前大江戶<br />\n我唔係話唔好食<br />\n而係佢扣單情況好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n唔好飲氣水<br />\n因為會搞到個肚好多氣好<br />\n<br />\n唔好食咁多 sushi <br />\n又係會令你易飽既食物"},{"pid":"9f84d8c316a2811e0dcf91f9e5aa53ca64ccf623","tid":760702,"uid":24024,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"留名睇一堆節墮窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c17242f267ca3a7181029ed41f667e68c1aef27","tid":760702,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"一開始叫炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0f08a8a434a3b4115b3da6ddf261aeab1a2f65","tid":760702,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953b57a7fd48b239cf1714a4d6249ff450bce877","tid":760702,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"我諗日式放題最貴都係魚生/海鮮類<br />\n<br />\n最好唔好去扣單既放題<br />\n例如觀塘x前大江戶<br />\n我唔係話唔好食<br />\n而係佢扣單情況好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n唔好飲氣水<br />\n因為會搞到個肚好多氣好<br />\n<br />\n唔好食咁多 sushi <br />\n又係會令你易